songs.title: Establo
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Sadboytaki & Nasty GX]
The school is fucked
The Fucking Teachers, the fucking authority, wow, you're right
Enclosed as animals, treated like garbage
But will we do something about it?

[Sadboytaki]
I will not come to say the kind of shit that is the school
"Writing" "Writing" is the only thing I hear, hear, hear, i hear
I will not talk about corruption, I will speak about my opinion

Come on, Come on, We have to reveal ourselves

The fucking school treats us like animals, and we're not
We are monsters who want the best, even if we do not deserve it

[Nasty GX]
Todos son tan... Estúpidos
La escuela... No ayudara

Si queremos algo mejor, tendremos que trabajar
Trabajar en algo mejor, sin horarios de 7 a 2

Vamos a ganar dinero enserio, ganar dinero así en seco
Queremos ser intelectuales, pero son mas que hábiles

Las Personas que ganan dinero fuero la escuela? Tal Vez

Pero adiós, ponte a estudia, o morirás
